hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Accountant supermarket manager viagra uk suppliers People then ask, legitimately, would it be possible to write honestly about The Club from the inside? “Who discovered Â water?” goes the old Yiddish riddle. “I don’t know, but it wasn’t a fish.” I am a fish. I have chosen to live, work, and raise my family in the murk. This might well be an easier pursuit for a citizen on solid land. But I have no plans to leave. People ask me about that too. Why? It’s not like I’m making lobbyist or TV money. I plead reality: my wife and I have built a good life here.
